Class YahooMediaGroup

Represents a means of grouping of YahooMediaContent objects that are effectively the same content, yet different representations.

Credits

Gets the entities that contributed to the creation of this media group.

Declaration
public Collection<YahooMediaCredit> Credits { get; }
Property Value
Type Description
System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection<YahooMediaCredit>

A System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection<T> collection of YahooMediaCredit objects that represent the entities that contributed to the creation of this media group. The default value is an empty collection.
Remarks

Current entities can include people, companies, locations, etc. Specific entities can have multiple roles, and several entities can have the same role. These should appear as distinct YahooMediaCredit entities.

TextSeries

Gets the text transcript, closed captioning, or lyrics for this media group.

Declaration
public Collection<YahooMediaText> TextSeries { get; }
Property Value
Type Description
System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection<YahooMediaText>

A System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection<T> collection of YahooMediaText objects that represent text transcript, closed captioning, or lyrics for this media group. The default value is an empty collection.
Remarks

Many of these YahooMediaText objects are permitted to provide a time series of text. In such cases, it is encouraged, but not required, that the YahooMediaText objects be grouped by language and appear in time sequence order based on the start time. YahooMediaText objects can have overlapping start and end times.

A System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection<T> collection of YahooMediaThumbnail objects that represent images that are representative of this media group. The default value is an empty collection.
Remarks

If multiple thumbnails are included, and time coding is not at play, it is assumed that the images are in order of importance.
